&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;People Leadership &amp;amp; Team Support:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;lead a team of ~12 assembly operators during daily production activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide hands-on training, OJT, and skill development to ensure operators follow Standardized Work and safety requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support operators in resolving quality, safety, or process-related issues; escalate when needed through proper channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cover operator tasks during breaks, absence, or emergencies to maintain line stability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver clear and continuous feedback to team members regarding performance, improvement areas, discipline, and development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a positive team environment that encourages communication, problem solving, and accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare work instructions for the assigned production line, working with Process Engineering to ensure accuracy and obtaining required approvals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Production &amp;amp; Quality Execution:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the completion of production targets in line with daily takt time and standard work expectations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Verify that all operators follow safety procedures, torque requirements, quality checkpoints, and process con

