&lt;li&gt;Ensure full compliance with all regulations, safety, and environmental standards related to logistics operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive continuous improvement initiatives using Lean, Six Sigma, and other process improvement methodologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement digital tools and analytics to enhance logistics visibility, planning, and decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
