&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We achieve this through deep vertical integration, with design, engineering, and production&amp;nbsp;happening in-house&amp;nbsp;across our global offices and&amp;nbsp;manufacturing&amp;nbsp;facilities.&amp;nbsp;Our&amp;nbsp;teams&amp;nbsp;come&amp;nbsp;from&amp;nbsp;industries&amp;nbsp;around the world, united by a shared commitment to excellence.&amp;nbsp;By refusing to settle, you&amp;nbsp;can&amp;nbsp;help&amp;nbsp;redefine&amp;nbsp;what’s&amp;nbsp;possible and&amp;nbsp;shape the future of mobility.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Lucid is excited to announce the grand opening of our brand-new Service Center in&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Mission Viejo, Ca&lt;/strong&gt; This new facility represents our continued investment in delivering an exceptional ownership experience and supporting the growing Lucid community throughout the region. We are building a talented team of service professionals who are passionate about innovation, customer excellence, and the future of sustainable transportation. Join us at an exciting time as we establish this state-of-the-art location and help shape the next chapter of Lucid&#39;s service operations from day one.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;: 28471 Marguerite Pkwy, Mission Viejo, CA 92692&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All employees will be trained at and report to our Costa Mesa Service center until the new site opens in Mission Viejo.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
